---
// Manifesto — the emotional thesis, type only, vast quiet space. Two-tone
// statement (ink leads, steel softens) so a single idea reads like a spread.
---

<section class="bg-sand">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-32 sm:px-10 sm:py-44">
    <p
      data-animate
      class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-mineral mb-12"
    >
      A quieter kind of confidence
    </p>
    <p
      data-animate
      class="max-w-4xl font-display text-3xl font-medium leading-[1.18] text-ink text-balance sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl"
    >
      The best businesses share a certain calm. Things simply work. Nothing
      rattles.
      <span class="text-steel">
        The technology underneath never asks for attention — it just holds,
        day after day. That calm is the thing we actually make.</span
      >
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
